OL,3,CPolice helicopter scrambled in
OL,4,CHeckmondwike stabbing horror
OL,6,FPolice are investigating a stabbing in
OL,7,FHeckmondwike last night.
OL,9,FWest Yorkshire Police officers and
OL,10,Fambulance service personnel attended
OL,11,Fan address on Lobley Street following
OL,12,Freports that a man had been stabbed.
OL,13,FThree people were taken to hospital,
OL,14,Faccording to the Yorkshire Ambulance
OL,15,FService.
OL,17,FThe emergency services were called out
OL,18,Fat around 10.20pm, West Yorkshire
OL,19,FPolice has confirmed. A spokesman said
OL,20,Fit was reported that a man had been
OL,21,Finjured in a stabbing incident.
